[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1172","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1172.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1540","title":"Cactus Software Shell Lock 弱加密导致源码泄露与权限提升漏洞","description":"Cactus Software Shell Lock（shell-lock）是一款将 shell 脚本转换为 ELF 二进制文件的工具，声称可隐藏原始脚本内容并提供 SUID root 执行能力。然而该工具使用极其简单的编码机制（交替加减 0x44 和 0x63）对 shell 脚本进行混淆，任何具有文件读权限的攻击者均可轻易解码还原原始 shell 源码。此外，当使用 shell-lock 生成的二进制文件被设置为 SUID root 时，程序在执行过程中会于 /var/tmp 目录（或 $TMPDIR 环境变量指定位置）创建临时文件并执行。由于临时文件无特殊权限，攻击者可利用竞争条件在程序执行前将其替换为指向 /bin/sh 的软链接，从而以 root 身份执行任意命令，完成本地权限提升。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1540"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Cactus Software 已确认该产品存在设计缺陷，未发布针对此弱编码和 SUID 竞争条件的正式补丁。建议停止使用 shell-lock 作为脚本混淆或 SUID 执行方案，改用 C 语言编写需要特权的程序，或通过 sudo 配置精细的权限控制。如现有环境中仍有 shell-lock 生成的二进制文件，应立即移除 SUID 位（chmod u-s），避免在受保护脚本中存放敏感凭据，并严格限制脚本文件访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93916168802365&w=2","http://www.atstake.com/research/advisories/1999/shell-lock.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3356","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1540.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c58m-4vx5-jf3r/GHSA-c58m-4vx5-jf3r.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1172.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1109","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0879","title":"Washington University WU-FTPD 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Washington University WU-FTPD 2.5.0 在处理 message 文件中的宏变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的包含恶意宏变量的 message 文件，触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 WU-FTPD 2.5.0 及相关的 FTP 服务器软件，CVSS v2.0 评分为 10.0，攻击复杂度低，危害等级严重。攻击者只需建立 FTP 连接并上传或触发包含超长宏变量的 message 文件即可完成利用，已有公开的远程利用代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0879"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.873","remediation":"WU-FTPD 已停止维护多年，官方未发布安全补丁。建议立即停止使用 WU-FTPD，迁移至受支持的替代 FTP 服务器软件，如 vsftpd 3.0.x、ProFTPD 1.3.x 或 Pure-FTPD 最新稳定版。如无法立即迁移，可在 ftpaccess 配置文件中禁用所有 message 文件处理功能，并在防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19560","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0879.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0879","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0879.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0879.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w87h-rw9r-9p4c/GHSA-w87h-rw9r-9p4c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0879.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000801.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wu_ftpd_overflow.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1019","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1236","title":"Internet Anywhere Mail Server 明文密码存储权限提升漏洞","description":"Internet Anywhere Mail Server 2.3.1 存在密码明文存储漏洞，该软件将用户密码以明文形式保存在 msgboxes.dbf 文件中，本地攻击者可读取该文件并直接获取明文密码，进而提升权限。此漏洞源于对敏感数据缺乏加密保护，属于本地利用，攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限。影响 Internet Anywhere Mail Server 2.3.1 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1236"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.530","remediation":"Internet Anywhere Mail Server 2.3.1 已将停止维护，无法通过官方补丁修复。建议立即迁移至受支持的邮件服务器（如 Postfix、Exim 或 Exchange Online），同时将 msgboxes.dbf 文件权限收紧为仅管理员可读（chmod 600），并排查已被本地低权限用户窃取的明文口令，及时修改关联账户密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9910&L=ntbugtraq&F=&S=&P=662","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/731","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3285","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1236.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1236","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1236.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1236.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7p62-2h53-pmjh/GHSA-7p62-2h53-pmjh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1236.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/731/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000802.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b1758a28-e205-4515-8328-4e8c6518192a.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0732","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0732.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0933","title":"TeamShare TeamTrack 3.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"TeamTrack Web 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 URL 请求，突破路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 TeamTrack 3.0 版本，可能导致敏感信息泄露，为后续攻击提供跳板。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0933"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.440","remediation":"建议升级 TeamTrack 至 3.0 以上已修复版本，或迁移至受支持的替代产品。如无法升级，应在 Web 服务器层配置 URL 重写规则，过滤 `../` 及 `..\\` 等目录遍历序列，并对用户输入的文件路径参数进行严格的白名单校验，拒绝包含路径分隔符的请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1096","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/689","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19537","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0933.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0933","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0933.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0933.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x85q-7g7w-wj4v/GHSA-x85q-7g7w-wj4v.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0933.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/112b6cf2eb30218e492a77c7d1bcb2220cd940b5/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0732.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0671","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0671.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0880","title":"University of Washington wu-ftpd SITE NEWER 内存耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"University of Washington 开发的 wu-ftpd FTP 服务器软件存在内存泄漏漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 SITE NEWER 命令，导致服务器无法正确释放已分配的内存，进而造成内存资源耗尽，最终引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 wu-ftpd 多个版本，远程未认证攻击者可利用此漏洞使服务崩溃，无需任何权限即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0880"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.987","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 SITE NEWER 命令的内存泄漏问题。如无法升级，建议迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在维护的 FTP 服务器软件，并在迁移前限制匿名用户的 SITE 命令执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0880","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0880.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0880","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0880.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b2