建议升级至更高版本或采取访问控制措施缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1500"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的邮件服务器软件。如仍需使用，应在防火墙或网络边界限制对 POP3 端口（默认 110）的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 段连接，并部署入侵检测系统监控异常 POP3 命令请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93880357530599&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/733"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1140.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0534","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0534.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0794","title":"Microsoft Excel SYLK格式文件宏处理不当漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 在处理符号链接（SYLK）格式文件时存在安全缺陷，当 SYLK 文件内嵌宏代码时，Excel 未向用户发出安全警告，导致宏代码可在用户不知情的情况下自动执行。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 及早期版本，攻击者可通过诱导用户打开精心制作的包含恶意宏的 SYLK 文件，在用户不知情的情况下执行任意宏代码，可能导致任意代码执行、数据窃取或系统破坏。攻击条件为受害者需打开攻击者构造的恶意 SYLK 文件，利用方式为通过电子邮件附件、网页下载或文件共享传播恶意 SYLK 文件诱导用户打开。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0794"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-044 对应的补丁（知识库文章 Q241900/Q241901/Q241902）。如无法立即更新，可在 Excel 选项中将宏安全级别设为“高”或“非常高”，禁止未经提示的宏自动执行，并避免打开来历不明的 SYLK 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241900","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241901","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241902","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-044"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0534.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1199","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1199.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1583","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9050,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 操作系统自带的 nslookup 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 nslookup 在解析和处理用户传入的 hostname 命令行参数时，未对输入长度进行边界校验，导致超长字符串会溢出预设缓冲区。本地已登录的普通用户可通过在命令行向 nslookup 传入超长 hostname 参数触发该溢出，从而覆盖相邻内存并劫持程序执行流，最终以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 AIX 4.3 版本的系统，攻击条件为攻击者在目标主机拥有本地登录或命令执行权限，无需远程网络访问即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1583"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:46.297","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的 AIX 4.3.3 后续补丁级别或 AIX 5L 版本；如暂无法升级，应限制普通用户对 nslookup 的执行权限（如移除 setuid 位、通过 sudo 限定授权用户），并避免以特权用户身份传入不可信的长 hostname 参数作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-1.ibm.com/support/search.wss?rs=0&q=IY02120&apar=only","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/872443","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/8031","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1583.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1583","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1583.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1583.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4h92-xfmc-824q/GHSA-4h92-xfmc-824q.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83038/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1583.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000799.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--dcde3665-1f4c-45ba-be37-257403a906b4.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1199.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1120","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1120.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1469","title":"Hughes miniSQL w3-auth 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"miniSQL 软件包中的 w3-auth CGI 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含超长 URL 或超长 User-Agent MIME 头的特制 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 miniSQL 软件包的系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1469"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:30.497","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 miniSQL 及其 w3-auth CGI 程序，该产品自 1999 年后已无安全更新。建议迁移至现代数据库方案（如 MySQL/MariaDB/PostgreSQL）并移除所有 w3-msql 相关 CGI 脚本。如因遗留系统无法立即迁移，应在 Web 服务器层面移除或禁用 w3-auth CGI 可执行权限，并在防火墙/反向代理中限制对该 CGI 的访问来源 IP，同时确保 HTTP_AUTHORIZATION 环境变量不被外部传入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93871926821410&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1469.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1469","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1469.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1469.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mv62-jpgw-4vgg/GHSA-mv62-jpgw-4vgg.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1469.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000798.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd2a79eb3e801a346d1f2affda8f984b2830c654/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1120.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0730","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0730.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0931","title":"MediaHouse Software Statistics Server 4.28/5.1 Server ID 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"MediaHouse Software Statistics Server 4.28 及 5.1 版本中存在基于栈的缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的超长 'Server ID' 参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区边界溢出，进而覆盖返回地址，最终实现远程代码执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，成功利用后可完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，建议用户升级至最新版本或应用厂商提供的补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0931"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.207","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 MediaHouse Software Statistics Server 4.28/5.1，厂商已无安全更新。建议立即停用该产品并迁移至受支持的替代统计服务软件。如无法立即迁移，应在网络边界防火墙配置规则，限制仅可信 IP 访问 Statistics Server 端口，并在应用层部署入侵检测系统（IDS）拦截包含超长 Server ID 字段的恶意请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/734","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19562","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8de487bef2c8b1936da1237463dc6052a1fcd655/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0931.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0931","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0931.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0931.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-956v-wm2r-68mw/GHSA-956v-wm2r-68mw.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/mediahouse_statistics_web_server.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0931.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b7356c2e-1829-404f-92e3-4ad5d2d0069d.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0730.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0730.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-09310","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-09310.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0931","title":"MediaHouse Software Statistics Server 'Server ID' 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"MediaHouse Software Statistics Server 4.28 和 5.1 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 Server ID 字段发送特制数据触发缓冲区溢出，进而导致拒绝服务或远程执行任意命令。攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络访问即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0931"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","avd"],"published":"1999-09-30","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议立即停用 MediaHouse Statistics Server，迁移至受支持的替代统计服务软件。如无法立即替换，应在防火墙层面限制对该服务端口的网络访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/734","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0931"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-09310.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1067","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1067.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1350","title":"ARCAD Systemhaus 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ARCAD Systemhaus 0.078-5 版本在安装关键程序和文件时设置了全局可写权限，本地攻击者可通过替换程序为特洛伊木马，从而获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 ARCAD Systemhaus 0.078-5 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1350"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-29","updated":"1999-09-29","remediation":"升级到 ARCAD Systemhaus 的最新版本，或手动修复受影响文件和目录的权限设置，确保关键程序和文件仅对授权用户可写。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93871933521519&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1067.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1069","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1352","title":"Linux Kernel mknod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux 2.2 内核中的 mknod 系统调用在处理符号链接时存在安全缺陷，未正确验证目标文件路径是否为符号链接，导致本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接并调用 mknod 覆盖系统关键文件，从而提升权限或破坏系统完整性。攻击者需拥有本地用户权限，无需其他特殊条件即可利用该漏洞实施权限提升攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1352"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.463","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 2.3.x 开发版中修复。如无法升级内核，可通过 LSM（Linux Security Module）如 SELinux 或 AppArmor 限制普通用户执行 mknod 系统调用权限，并设置 /proc/sys/fs/protected_hardlinks 为 1 增强链接保护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93855134409747&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1352","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1352.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x7c6-rhq3-252p/GHSA-x7c6-rhq3-252p.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1352.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000795.txt","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1069.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1069.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0789","title":"IBM AIX ftpd libc 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3.2 操作系统 ftpd 服务所依赖的 libc 库在处理用户输入时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，根源在于未进行有效的边界长度检查，导致超长输入可覆盖栈内存。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送特制的超长参数触发溢出，破坏程序执行流程进而执行任意代码或造成拒绝服务。攻击者只需能够访问目标 TCP 21 端口即可发起攻击，无需有效凭证，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0789"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-28","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3.3 或后续已修复版本，并向 IBM 申请安装针对该 ftpd/libc 缓冲区溢出的官方 APAR 补丁（如 IY01919 等系列）。若暂无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 ftp 行后执行 refresh -s inetd 临时禁用 ftpd 服务，或通过防火墙限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 TCP 21 端口作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-072.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/679","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19532","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0789.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8057fa2fdc38632692a6b3f836dd95e1eb8504fd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0789.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0789.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-25cr-8qvj-rg6f/GHSA-25cr-8qvj-rg6f.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/aix_ftpd.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0789.json"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19532","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0789.md"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19532"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0709.toml"}]